{"tid":966551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑衣男蘋果大樓淋油","createTime":"2019-01-03T01:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T06:34:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"18faa61e90c8794e1e38bf8af40e76eca21f117f","tid":966551,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:33:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190103/20582645\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F20582645&d=LzYF7DbOJ2VHvfr96iZeNP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=50f35518\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F20582645&h=cb656821\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190103/20582645</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月03日 <br />\n<br />\n黑衣男蘋果大樓淋油<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190103/large/03la8p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190103%2Flarge%2F03la8p05.jpg&h=05173c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n壹蘋果大樓閘門外被貼上大字報及潑紅油。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名男子昨凌晨徒步到將軍澳壹蘋果大樓，在大閘外貼「大字報」然後潑上紅油，男子拍照留紀錄後跑步逃離現場，至早上一名職員上班時發現並通知保安員，經翻查閉路電視片段後，保安員報警。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n閘外貼警告字句<br />\n<br />\n現場為將軍澳工業邨駿盈街壹蘋果大樓A閘門，大閘外被人貼上一張A4紙及淋紅油，大閘門鐘、牆身及地面都沾有紅油。昨晨5時許，一名職員上班時發現情況通知保安員，保安員經請示上級後至早上近8時報警。警員到場調查，發現沾有紅油的A4紙以黑色筆寫上警告字句，抬頭是「給總編緝」，內容大致要求不要再報道有關某金融集團的新聞。<br />\n<br />\n警方翻查閉路電視片段，發現昨凌晨2時許，一名黑衣男子，徒步走到壹蘋果大樓A閘門外，貼上A4紙後再用白色杯盛載的紅油淋向閘門，事後拍照留紀錄，淋油男子其後跑離現場，全程約一分鐘。警方將案件列作刑事毀壞，交由將軍澳警區重案組接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃江奇  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n行山客墮五米崖重創<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n民陣反擊政府公民廣場禁「獨」「不做打壓人權幫兇」"},{"pid":"737eb61268a95fc3e17828ef72570b26ce1df82b","tid":966551,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:36:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d98dce4e33cfb659ef9b9ffd54222b84fba34db0","tid":966551,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"男子拍照留紀錄後跑步逃離現場<br />\n<br />\n得一條友鳩流流連車都無，間公司一定比唔夠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b47d4f705cdcaf486b4356f9569f3d9bf11279","tid":966551,"uid":165735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:55:19.000Z","msg":"淋得兩滴. 無吉屎."},{"pid":"bf8e1d175366499a0527f8258cb62b36d4d59690","tid":966551,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d98dce4e33cfb659ef9b9ffd54222b84fba34db0","tid":966551,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"男子拍照留紀錄後跑步逃離現場<br />\n<br />\n得一條友鳩流流連車都無，間公司一定比唔夠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T02:04:12.000Z","msg":"二判再三判最後咪得咁既貨仔"},{"pid":"28e92ef25ab587437e2d9735f846984d6b7237c4","tid":966551,"uid":190383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T02:42:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人知係邊間公司？"},{"pid":"1eb89056dfa5ca4ca17f93eddf4303410a0cb17a","tid":966551,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWkHesT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWkHesT.gif&h=c45c6f93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來一早預言左,真係出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c45673681c8a06d7dfd488e22978e923a687e2","tid":966551,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"2019 年重淋油 .. 比 D 新意啦屌"},{"pid":"676d2635b16deea5bcb2be16028b329e8362f3a8","tid":966551